data.title: Announcement of the candidates for election to the office of the President: extracts
data.meta_description: Announcement of the candidates for election to the office of the President of the European Parliament, during the EP plenary session (16-19 January) in Strasbourg. The names of the candidates are Eleonora Forenza (European United Left-Nordic Green Left Group, Italy) Jean Lambert, (Group of the Greens/European Free Alliance, UK), Gianni Pittella, (Progressive Alliance of Socialists and Democrats Group, Italy), Lauren≈£iu Rebega, (Europe of Nations and Freedom Group, Romania), Helga Stevens, (European Conservatives and Reformists Group, Belgium), Antonio Tajani, European People’s Party Group (Italy) and Guy Verhofstadt, (Group of the Alliance of Liberals and Democrats for Europe, Belgium).
